<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>CSRF 驗證失敗</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: #f9fafb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
            color: #1c1c1c;
        }
        .error-card {
            max-width: 560px;
            background: #fff;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #b42318;
        }
        p {
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .actions {
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        a.button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: #2563eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-card">
        <h1>驗證失敗</h1>
        <p>{{message}}</p>
        <p>請重新整理頁面或返回後台重新登入後再試一次。</p>
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/admin/login" class="button">返回登入</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
